=== 恒星 ===
{{see also|时钟座恒星列表}}
时钟座只有一颗星亮度超过4.0[[视星等|视星等]]<ref name="cambridge">{{cite book | last1 = Moore | first1 = Patrick | last2 = Tirion | first2 = Wil | title = Cambridge Guide to Stars and Planets | publisher = [[劍橋大學出版社|Cambridge University Press]] | location = Cambridge, UK | year = 1997 | access-date = 2021-01-16 | page = [https://archive.org/details/cambridgeguideto00moor/page/190 190] | isbn = 978-0521585828 | url = https://archive.org/details/cambridgeguideto00moor}}</ref>，41颗达到或超过6.5视星等{{refn|group="注"|6.5视星等是肉眼在城乡结合位置理想夜空条件下能看到的光线最微弱天体<ref>{{cite web | url = https://skyandtelescope.org/astronomy-resources/light-pollution-and-astronomy-the-bortle-dark-sky-scale/ | title = Gauging Light Pollution: The Bortle Dark-Sky Scale | last = Bortle | first = John E. | date = 2006-07-18 | work = [[天空與望遠鏡雜誌|Sky & Telescope]] | publisher = Sky Publishing Corporation | access-date = 2015-08-01 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190408163545/https://www.skyandtelescope.com/astronomy-resources/light-pollution-and-astronomy-the-bortle-dark-sky-scale/ | archive-date = 2019-04-08 | dead-url = no}}</ref>。}}<ref name="tirionconst" />。1756年拉卡伊将星座中11颗恒星标上星图，并以[[拜耳命名法|拜耳命名法]]分配[[天园增六|α]]至[[時鐘座λ|λ]]共11个[[希腊字母|希腊字母]]。19世纪中期，英格兰天文学家[[弗朗西斯·贝利|弗朗西斯·贝利]]撤消ε和θ两个字母，认为这两颗恒星过于黯淡，不够资格获名。他在拉卡伊划定的[[時鐘座β|時鐘座β]]位置没有找到恒星，认为坐标有误，将名称分给其他恒星。时钟座κ的位置同样没有恒星，名称因此停用，估计很可能是指HD 18292。1879年，美国天文学家[[本杰明·阿普索普·古尔德|本杰明·阿普索普·古尔德]]认为另外两颗恒星亮度足以分配希腊字母，这便是如今的[[時鐘座μ|時鐘座μ]]和[[時鐘座ν|時鐘座ν]]。<ref name="wagman" />

时钟座以3.85视星等的[[天园增六|天园增六]]最亮，距地球115±0.5[[光年|光年]]<ref name="vanLeeuwen2007">{{cite journal | first = F. | last = van Leeuwen | title = Validation of the New Hipparcos Reduction | journal = Astronomy and Astrophysics | volume = 474 | issue = 2 | pages = 653–664 | year = 2007 | bibcode = 2007A&A...474..653V | doi = 10.1051/0004-6361:20078357 | arxiv = 0708.1752}}</ref>。德国天文学家[[约翰·波得|约翰·波得]]认为该星代表钟摆，拉卡伊将其视为钟摆砝码<ref name="ridphor">{{cite web | url = http://www.ianridpath.com/startales/horologium.html | title = Horologium | work = Star Tales | last = Ridpath | first = Ian | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201025020747/http://ianridpath.com/startales/horologium.html | publisher = self-published | access-date = 2021-01-16 | archive-date = 2020-10-25 | dead-url = no}}</ref>，是[[恒星分类|光谱等级]]{{lang|en|K2III}}的老化橙[[巨星|巨星]]，已膨胀到约11倍太阳直径，[[A型主序星|白主序星]]阶段已过去大半<ref name="kaleralfa">{{cite web | last = Kaler | first = Jim | title = Alpha Horologii | archive-date = 2020-11-05 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201105143247/http://stars.astro.illinois.edu/sow/alphahor.html | url = http://stars.astro.illinois.edu/sow/alphahor.html | dead-url = no | website = James Kaler's Stars | access-date = 2021-01-16}}</ref>。估计该星拥有1.55倍[[太阳质量|太阳质量]]<ref name="Liu 2007">{{cite journal | last1 = Liu | first1 = Y. J. | last2 = Zhao | first2 = G. | last3 = Shi | first3 = J. R. | last4 = Pietrzyński | first4 = G. | last5 = Gieren | first5 = W. | year = 2007 | title = The Abundances of Nearby Red Clump Giants | journal = Monthly Notices of the Royal Astronomical Society | volume = 382 | issue = 2 | pages = 553–566 | bibcode = 2007MNRAS.382..553L | doi = 10.1111/j.1365-2966.2007.11852.x}}</ref>，[[光球|光球]]辐射量达38倍[[太陽光度|太陽光度]]，表面[[有效溫度|有效溫度]]5028[[开尔文|开尔文]]<ref name="Mcdonald">{{cite journal | last1 = McDonald | first1 = I. | last2 = Zijlstra | first2 = A. A. | last3 = Boyer | first3 = M. L. | year = 2012 | title = Fundamental Parameters and Infrared Excesses of Hipparcos Stars | journal = Monthly Notices of the Royal Astronomical Society | volume = 427 | issue = 1 | pages = 343–357 | bibcode = 2012MNRAS.427..343M | arxiv = 1208.2037 | doi = 10.1111/j.1365-2966.2012.21873.x}}</ref>。

4.93视星等的[[時鐘座δ|時鐘座δ]]是时钟座第二亮恒星<ref name="kalerbeta">{{cite web | last = Kaler | first = Jim | title = Beta Horologii | url = http://stars.astro.illinois.edu/sow/betahor.html | website = James Kaler's Stars | date = 2011-01-21 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200801164234/http://stars.astro.illinois.edu/sow/betahor.html | archive-date = 2020-08-01 | dead-url = no | access-date = 2021-01-16}}</ref>，与天园增六组成范围宽大的[[雙星|光学双星]]<ref name="arnold">{{cite book | last1 = Arnold | first1 = H.J.P | last2 = Doherty | first2 = Paul | last3 = Moore | first3 = Patrick | title = The Photographic Atlas of the Stars | publisher = CRC Press | location = Boca Raton, Florida | year = 1999 | url = https://books.google.com.tw/books?id=YjcvJUfnWBAC&pg=PA48&redir_esc=y#v=onepage&q&f=false | page = 48 | isbn = 978-0750306546 | access-date = 2021-01-16 | archive-date = 2021-02-07 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210207125146/https://books.google.com.tw/books?id=YjcvJUfnWBAC&pg=PA48&redir_esc=y#v=onepage&q&f=false | dead-url = no }}</ref>。时钟座δ是[[聯星|聯星]]系统，主星光谱等级{{lang|en|A5V}}，是1.41倍太阳质量、5.15视星等的白主序星；伴星7.29视星等<ref name="Eggleton2008">{{cite journal | last1 = Eggleton | first1 = P. P. | last2 = Tokovinin | first2 = A. A. | title = A Catalogue of Multiplicity among Bright Stellar Systems | journal = [[皇家天文學會月報|Monthly Notices of the Royal Astronomical Society]] | volume = 389 | issue = 2 | pages = 869–879 | year = 2008 | doi = 10.1111/j.1365-2966.2008.13596.x | bibcode = 2008MNRAS.389..869E | arxiv = 0806.2878 }}</ref>，联星距地球179±4光年<ref name="vanLeeuwen2007" />。

5.0视星等的时钟座β是白巨星，光度达太阳63倍，表面有效温度8303K<ref name="Mcdonald" />，距地球312±4光年<ref name="GaiaDR2beta">{{cite DR2|4720282071779657600}}</ref>，人类目前还缺乏了解<ref name="kalerbeta" />。时钟座λ是光谱等级{{lang|en|F2III}}的老化黄白巨星，距地球161±1光年<ref name="vanLeeuwen2007" />，以每秒140公里的速度旋转，因此两极略显拉平，呈[[類球面|扁球状]]）<ref name="belle">{{Cite journal | doi = 10.1007/s00159-012-0051-2| title = Interferometric Observations of Rapidly Rotating Stars| year = 2012 | last1 = Belle | first1 = G. T. | journal = The Astronomy and Astrophysics Review | volume = 20 | issue = 1 | page = 51 | bibcode = 2012A&ARv..20...51V | arxiv = 1204.2572}}</ref>。

時鐘座ν是5.24视星等的白主序星<ref name="apj800_1_5"/>，光谱等级{{lang|en|A2V}}，距地球169±1光年<ref name="GaiaDR2nu">{{cite DR2|4721400206385912960}}</ref>，有约1.9倍太阳质量。估计该星已有5.4亿年历史，[[岩屑盤|岩屑盤]]包含两部分：内盘轨道距恒星{{val|96|+9|−37|u=[[天文單位|天文單位]]}}，外盘距恒星{{val|410|+24|−96|u= AU}}。估计岩屑盘质量为地球{{val|0.13|±0.07|u=%}}<ref name="apj800_1_5">{{cite journal | last1 = Meshkat | first1 = Tiffany | last2 = Bailey | first2 = Vanessa P. | last3 = Su | first3 = Kate Y. L. | last4 = Kenworthy | first4 = Matthew A. | last5 = Mamajek | first5 = Eric E. | last6 = Hinz | first6 = Philip M. | last7 = Smith | first7 = Paul S. | title = Searching for Planets in Holey Debris Disks with the Apodizing Phase Plate | journal = The Astrophysical Journal | volume = 800 | issue = 1 | id = 5 | year = 2015 | doi = 10.1088/0004-637X/800/1/5 | bibcode = 2015ApJ...800....5M | arxiv = 1412.5179 | page = 5}}</ref>。

时钟座[[變星|變星]]众多。[[紅巨星|紅巨星]][[時鐘座R|時鐘座R]]便是[[刍藁变星|刍藁变星]]，亮度变化幅度之大在夜空所有肉眼可见的恒星中名列前茅<ref name="privett">{{cite book | last1 = Privett | first1 = Grant | last2 = Jones | first2 = Kevin | title = The Constellation Observing Atlas | publisher = [[施普林格科学+商业媒体|Springer Science & Business Media]] | location = New York | year = 2013 | page = 102 | isbn = 978-1461476481 | url = https://books.google.com.tw/books?id=uN69BAAAQBAJ&pg=PA102&redir_esc=y#v=onepage&q&f=false | access-date = 2021-01-16 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160328183439/https://books.google.com.au/books?id=uN69BAAAQBAJ&pg=PA102 | archive-date = 2016-03-28 | dead-url = no}}</ref>，距地球约一千光年<ref name="GaiaDR2r">{{cite DR2|4748477123328077696}}</ref>。该星亮度以13个月为周期在14.3至4.7视星等范围变化<ref name="ridpath2017">{{cite book | first1 = Ian | last1 = Ridpath | first2 = Wil | last2 = Tirion | year = 2017| title = Stars and Planets Guide | publisher = Collins | location = London | isbn = 978-0-00-823927-5 | page = 158}}</ref>。时钟座T和时钟座U也是刍藁变星<ref name="arnold" />，[[南非天文学会|南非天文学会]]于2003年宣布两星[[光變曲線|光變曲線]]数据不完整，需要进一步观测<ref name="cooper">{{cite journal | last = Cooper | first = Tim | year = 2003 | title = Presidential Address: Amateur Observations – Successes and Opportunities | journal = Monthly Notes of the Astronomical Society of Southern Africa | volume = 62 | pages = 234–240 | bibcode = 2003MNSSA..62..234C}}</ref>。红巨星[[時鐘座TW|時鐘座TW]]是[[半規則變星|半規則變星]]，也是[[碳星|碳星]]<ref name="ridpath2017" />，距地球1370±70光年<ref name="GaiaDR2tw">{{cite DR2|4727337637895749888}}</ref>。

黄白矮星[[时钟座ι|时钟座ι]]拥有1.23±0.12倍太阳质量，1.16±0.04倍太阳直径，光谱等级{{lang|en|F8V}}<ref name="Bruntt2010">{{cite journal | title = Accurate Fundamental Parameters for 23 Bright Solar-type Stars | last1 = Bruntt | first1 = H. | last2 = Bedding | first2 = T. R. | last3 = Quirion | first3 = P.-O. | last4 = Lo Curto | first4 = G. | last5 = Carrier | first5 = F. | last6 = Smalley | first6 = B. | last7 = Dall | first7 = T. H. | last8 = Arentoft | first8 = T. | last9 = Bazot | first9 = M. | journal = Monthly Notices of the Royal Astronomical Society | volume = 405 | issue = 3 | pages = 1907–1923 | year = 2010 | arxiv = 1002.4268 | bibcode = 2010MNRAS.405.1907B | doi = 10.1111/j.1365-2966.2010.16575.x}}</ref>，与地球相隔57±0.05光年<ref name="Gaia DR2iota">{{Cite DR2|4745373133284418816}}</ref>。从化学组成、运动和年龄判断，该星在[[畢宿星團|畢宿星團]]形成，但已飘移到其他星球约130光年外<ref name="Vauclair2008">{{cite journal | title = The Exoplanet-host Star Iota Horologii: an Evaporated Member of the Primordial Hyades Cluster | last1 = Vauclair | first1 = S. | last2 = Laymand | first2 = M. | last3 = Bouchy | first3 = F. | last4 = Vauclair | first4 = G. | last5 = Hui Bon Hoa | first5 = A. | last6 = Charpinet | first6 = S. | last7 = Bazot | first7 = M. | journal = Astronomy and Astrophysics | volume = 482 | issue = 2 | pages = L5–L8 | year = 2008 | arxiv = 0803.2029 | bibcode = 2008A&A...482L...5V | doi = 10.1051/0004-6361:20079342}}</ref>，周围有至少2.5倍[[木星|木星]]质量的行星旋转，轨道周期307天<ref name="Zechmeister2013">{{cite journal | title = The Planet Search Programme at the ESO CES and HARPS. IV. The Search for Jupiter Analogues around Solar-like Stars | last1 = Zechmeister | first1 = M. | last2 = Kürster | first2 = M. | last3 = Endl | first3 = M. | last4 = Lo Curto | first4 = G. | last5 = Hartman | first5 = H. | last6 = Nilsson | first6 = H. | last7 = Henning | first7 = T. | last8 = Hatzes | first8 = A. P. | last9 = Cochran | first9 = W. D. | journal = Astronomy and Astrophysics | volume = 552 | at = A78 | year = 2013 | bibcode = 2013A&A...552A..78Z | arxiv = 1211.7263 | doi = 10.1051/0004-6361/201116551 }}</ref>。[[HD_27631|HD 27631]]是类日恒星，距地球164±0.3光年<ref name="GaiaDR2HD27631">{{cite DR2|4840050395924931968}}</ref>，拥有至少1.45倍木星质量的行星，公转周期2208天<ref name="Marmier2013">{{cite journal | title = The CORALIE Survey for Southern Extrasolar Planets XVII. New and Updated Long Period and Massive Planets | last1 = Marmier | first1 = M. | last2 = Ségransan | first2 = D. | last3 = Udry | first3 = S. | last4 = Mayor | first4 = M. | last5 = Pepe | first5 = F. | last6 = Queloz | first6 = D. | last7 = Lovis | first7 = C. | last8 = Naef | first8 = D. | last9 = Santos | first9 = N. C. | last10 = Alonso | first10 = R. | last11 = Alves | first11 = S. | last12 = Berthet | first12 = S. | last13 = Chazelas | first13 = B. | last14 = Demory | first14 = B.-O. | last15 = Dumusque | first15 = X. | last16 = Eggenberger | first16 = A. | last17 = Figueira | first17 = P. | last18 = Gillon | first18 = M. | last19 = Hagelberg | first19 = J. | last20 = Lendl | first20 = M. | last21 = Mardling | first21 = R. A. | last22 = Mégevand | first22 = D. | last23 = Neveu | first23 = M. | last24 = Sahlmann | first24 = J. | last25 = Sosnowska | first25 = D. | last26 = Tewes | first26 = M. | last27 = Triaud | first27 = A. H. M. J. | journal = Astronomy and Astrophysics | volume = 551 | at = A90 | year = 2013 | arxiv = 1211.6444 | bibcode = 2013A&A...551A..90M | doi = 10.1051/0004-6361/201219639 }}</ref>。WASP-120是约1.4倍太阳质量的黄白主序星，光谱等级{{lang|en|F5V}}，估计已有26±5亿年历史。该星的行星质量达4.85倍木星，每3.6天就能公转一周，估计表面温度达1880±70K<ref name="turner">{{Cite journal | bibcode = 2016PASP..128f4401T | title = WASP-120 b, WASP-122 b, and WASP-123 b: Three Newly Discovered Planets from the WASP-South Survey | journal = Publications of the Astronomical Society of the Pacific | volume = 128 | issue = 964 | pages = 064401 | last1 = Turner | first1 = O. D | last2 = Anderson | first2 = D. R | last3 = Collier Cameron | first3 = A | last4 = Delrez | first4 = L | last5 = Evans | first5 = D. F | last6 = Gillon | first6 = M | last7 = Hellier | first7 = C | last8 = Jehin | first8 = E | last9 = Lendl | first9 = M | last10 = Maxted | first10 = P. F. L | last11 = Pepe | first11 = F | last12 = Pollacco | first12 = D | last13 = Queloz | first13 = D | last14 = Ségransan | first14 = D | last15 = Smalley | first15 = B | last16 = Smith | first16 = A. M. S | last17 = Triaud | first17 = A. H. M. J | last18 = Udry | first18 = S | last19 = West | first19 = R. G | year = 2016 | doi = 10.1088/1538-3873/128/964/064401 | arxiv = 1509.02210}}</ref>。

13.06视星等的[[紅矮星|紅矮星]][[格利澤1061|格利澤1061]]光谱等级{{lang|en|M5.5V}}，质量和直径分别是太阳的一成二和一成五，光度仅0.17%，距地球12光年，属离太阳最近的20颗单星或恒星系统。2019年8月，科学家宣布该星有三颗行星，其中一颗位于[[適居帶|適居帶]]。<ref>{{Cite journal | last = Anglada-Escudé | first = G. | last2 = Reiners | first2 = A. | last3 = Pallé | first3 = E. | last4 = Ribas | first4 = I. | last5 = Berdiñas | first5 = Z. M. | last6 = López | first6 = C. Rodríguez | last7 = Morales | first7 = N. | last8 = López-González | first8 = M. J. | last9 = Hambsch | first9 = F.-J. | date = 2019-08-13 | title = Red Dots: A Temperate 1.5 Earth-mass Planet in a Compact Multi-terrestrial Planet System around GJ1061 | doi = 10.1093/mnras/staa248 | journal = Monthly Notices of the Royal Astronomical Society | arxiv = 1908.04717 | volume = 493 | issue = 1 | pages = 536–550}}</ref>

=== 深空天体 ===
[[File:NGC_1512_and_NGC_1510.jpg|thumb]]（左）[[棒旋星系|棒旋星系]]和[[NGC_1510|NGC 1510]][[矮星系|矮星系]]的合成图像]]

时钟座[[深空天體|深空天體]]众多，其中不乏[[球狀星團|球狀星團]]。[[NGC_1261|NGC 1261]]是8.0视星等的球状星团，与地球相隔5.3万光年<ref name="ridpath2017" />，位于时钟座μ东北偏北4.7度<ref name="bakich" />。[[阿普-马多雷一号|阿普-马多雷一号]]（{{lang|en|Arp-Madore 1}}）距地球40.2万光年，是[[银河系|银河系]]内确知距离最远的球状星团<ref>{{Cite journal | doi = 10.1093/mnras/stz171 | title = Proper Motions and Dynamics of the Milky Way Globular Cluster System from Gaia DR2 | journal = Monthly Notices of the Royal Astronomical Society | volume = 484 | issue = 2 | pages = 2832–2850 | year = 2019 | last = Vasiliev | first = Eugene | bibcode = 2019MNRAS.484.2832V | arxiv = 1807.09775}}</ref>。

[[NGC_1512|NGC 1512]]是天园增六西南偏西2.1度的[[棒旋星系|棒旋星系]]，亮度10.2视星等<ref name="bakich">{{cite book | title = 1001 Celestial Wonders to See Before You Die: The Best Sky Objects for Star Gazers | url = https://archive.org/details/celestialwonders00baki_175 | first = Michael E. | last = Bakich | publisher = Springer | year = 2010 | isbn = 978-1441917775 | pages = [https://archive.org/details/celestialwonders00baki_175/page/n414 402], 416}}</ref>，与[[矮星系|矮]][[透鏡狀星系|透鏡狀星系]][[NGC_1510|NGC 1510]]相隔约五[[弧分|弧分]]（13.8[[秒差距|秒差距]]）。两个星系从约四亿年前就开始逐渐合并<ref name="Monthly400">{{cite journal | last1 = Koribalski | first1 = Bärbel S. | last2 = López-Sánchez | first2 = Ángel R. | year = 2009 | title = Gas Dynamics and Star Formation in the Galaxy Pair NGC 1512/1510 | journal = Monthly Notices of the Royal Astronomical Society | volume = 400 | issue = 4 | page = 21 | doi = 10.1111/j.1365-2966.2009.15610.x | arxiv = 0908.4128 | bibcode = 2009MNRAS.400.1749K}}</ref>。

[[时钟座超星系团|时钟座超星系团]]是地球周边两百[[秒差距|秒差距]]范围内的第二大[[超星系团|超星系团]]，规模仅次于[[夏普力超星系團|夏普力超星系團]]，覆盖上百平方度天空，拥有二十多个[[阿贝尔星系团表|阿贝尔星系团]]，中心位于赤道坐標系統α={{RA|03|19}}，δ={{DEC|50|2}}左右<ref name="apj130_3">{{cite journal | last1 = Fleenor | first1 = Matthew C. | last2 = Rose | first2 = James A. | last3 = Christiansen | first3 = Wayne A. | last4 = Hunstead | first4 = Richard W. | last5 = Johnston-Hollitt | first5 = Melanie | last6 = Drinkwater | first6 = Michael J. | last7 = Saunders | first7 = William | title = Large-Scale Velocity Structures in the Horologium-Reticulum Supercluster | journal = The Astronomical Journal | volume = 130 | issue = 3 | pages = 957–967 | date = 2005-09 | doi = 10.1086/431972 | bibcode = 2005AJ....130..957F | arxiv = astro-ph/0505361 }}</ref>。

